lyrics:
[Verse]
In this world of blocks, where dreams ignite
One block at a time, we embrace the light
With every strike, a vision takes form
Expanding our realm, weathering the storm

[Chorus]
One block, one world, boundless horizons we see
Crafting our legacy, in this tapestry
Infinite potential, in our hands stark
One block at a time, shaping our mark
